{"tid":2009770,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"而家既微辣有咩咁正","createTime":"2020-05-10T04:00:38.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-10T08:01:26.000Z","uid":199570,"like":13,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"cf9fdd3674b2e7f2da3c58e64949cc5238bf472e","tid":2009770,"uid":199570,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-10T04:00:38.000Z","msg":"啱啱搭巴士見到有個細路睇緊微辣<br />\n仲笑得勁大聲<br />\n好似睇得好開心咁<br />\n之後佢仲遞部電話過去迫佢阿媽一齊睇<br />\n仲邊睇邊講解俾佢阿媽聽<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我嗰刻feel到佢阿媽完全係笑而不語<br />\n心諗咁on9既片你都笑得出<br />\n<br />\n想知微辣而家係咪已經變左專攻小學雞市場<br />\n想挑戰大j既霸主地位<br />\n當大j多左好多連登仔支持既時候<br />\n微辣多既反而係小學雞fans<br />\n<br />\n以量取勝<br />\n高質不再<br />\n幾時先俾返最初頭既微辣我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"594bdcea8728943b1049b6f763ba362315867fa1","tid":2009770,"uid":247719,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-10T04:01:07.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"6850677d9950dfc97f6eee808a8cf5c2cb28ee82","tid":2009770,"uid":345989,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-10T04:02:37.000Z","msg":"講到初頭好似好高質咁"},{"pid":"101b5d4a8fa99bf79bf2d9165799e1c7606cf360","tid":2009770,"uid":237237,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-10T04:02:57.000Z","msg":"唔係你仲想咩人睇 而家啲片內容唔係食字gag就係講中學生活 拍拖 咸濕野<br />\n睇綜藝仲好笑過睇短片"},{"pid":"3eaf66d428f29535b552237b629b406c7cff8a7d","tid":2009770,"uid":124667,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"101b5d4a8fa99bf79bf2d9165799e1c7606cf360","tid":2009770,"uid":237237,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-10T04:02:57.000Z","msg":"唔係你仲想咩人睇 而家啲片內容唔係食字gag就係講中學生活 拍拖 咸濕野<br />\n睇綜藝仲好笑過睇短片"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-10T04:05:48.000Z","msg":"綜藝好睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\